cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the interaction between humans and robots, specifically in the context of EEG signal analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also involves robotics and machine learning, which suggests cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as likely categories. The use of deep convolutional neural networks (ConvNets) for EEG signal analysis suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible category. Finally, the visualization of EEG features learned by the ConvNets suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as a possible category.
